[
  {
    "text": "this is how cement tiles are handmade",
    "start": 2.159,
    "duration": 4.801
  },
  {
    "text": "at one of the few workshops left in",
    "start": 5.04,
    "duration": 3.599
  },
  {
    "text": "egypt",
    "start": 6.96,
    "duration": 3.2
  },
  {
    "text": "the craft has been around since the",
    "start": 8.639,
    "duration": 4.561
  },
  {
    "text": "1800s when cement became a cheap and",
    "start": 10.16,
    "duration": 6.08
  },
  {
    "text": "efficient way to build",
    "start": 13.2,
    "duration": 7.76
  },
  {
    "text": "but for syed hussein it's an art form",
    "start": 16.24,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "even though other types of tiles have",
    "start": 25.439,
    "duration": 3.121
  },
  {
    "text": "threatened his business",
    "start": 27.119,
    "duration": 3.261
  },
  {
    "text": "he's stayed true to his trade",
    "start": 28.56,
    "duration": 3.119
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 30.38,
    "duration": 5.46
  },
  {
    "text": "plan we visited cairo",
    "start": 31.679,
    "duration": 8.001
  },
  {
    "text": "to see how his workshop is still",
    "start": 35.84,
    "duration": 3.84
  },
  {
    "text": "standing",
    "start": 42.84,
    "duration": 3.239
  },
  {
    "text": "syed has been making tiles since he was",
    "start": 44.079,
    "duration": 3.601
  },
  {
    "text": "12 years old",
    "start": 46.079,
    "duration": 3.521
  },
  {
    "text": "and much of his process is still the",
    "start": 47.68,
    "duration": 2.93
  },
  {
    "text": "same",
    "start": 49.6,
    "duration": 4.04
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 50.61,
    "duration": 3.03
  },
  {
    "text": "um",
    "start": 56.84,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "he begins with sifting white cement",
    "start": 61.68,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 65.12,
    "duration": 3.84
  },
  {
    "text": "once it's become a fine powder he mixes",
    "start": 66.4,
    "duration": 6.48
  },
  {
    "text": "in pigments to get just the right hue",
    "start": 68.96,
    "duration": 7.839
  },
  {
    "text": "working with colors is his speciality",
    "start": 72.88,
    "duration": 3.919
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 77.05,
    "duration": 3.17
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 82.59,
    "duration": 3.129
  },
  {
    "text": "then he adds in water",
    "start": 95.52,
    "duration": 6.32
  },
  {
    "text": "syed pours each color into its own",
    "start": 102.24,
    "duration": 5.519
  },
  {
    "text": "section using one of his stencils",
    "start": 104.32,
    "duration": 11.52
  },
  {
    "text": "he's had these for over 35 years",
    "start": 107.759,
    "duration": 8.081
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 115.97,
    "duration": 8.189
  },
  {
    "text": "he worked slowly and precisely to",
    "start": 121.84,
    "duration": 5.76
  },
  {
    "text": "navigate the finer details",
    "start": 124.159,
    "duration": 3.441
  },
  {
    "text": "foreign",
    "start": 140.84,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 151.07,
    "duration": 3.17
  },
  {
    "text": "foreign",
    "start": 154.84,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 158.0,
    "duration": 13.84
  },
  {
    "text": "some designs syed does freehand",
    "start": 166.16,
    "duration": 5.68
  },
  {
    "text": "he tops off the mold with a mixture of",
    "start": 177.68,
    "duration": 4.4
  },
  {
    "text": "sand cement and limestone",
    "start": 179.519,
    "duration": 4.401
  },
  {
    "text": "a crucial step to ensure the pattern",
    "start": 182.08,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "stays in place",
    "start": 183.92,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 189.75,
    "duration": 3.06
  },
  {
    "text": "then he sends it through the hydraulic",
    "start": 195.12,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": "press",
    "start": 197.04,
    "duration": 4.4
  },
  {
    "text": "the machine's pressure solidifies the",
    "start": 199.76,
    "duration": 4.88
  },
  {
    "text": "cement within seconds",
    "start": 201.44,
    "duration": 3.2
  },
  {
    "text": "syed learned this craft from his father",
    "start": 206.0,
    "duration": 3.36
  },
  {
    "text": "who worked at a shop",
    "start": 208.319,
    "duration": 4.161
  },
  {
    "text": "owned by greek immigrants",
    "start": 209.36,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "have roots in other parts of europe too",
    "start": 225.04,
    "duration": 4.88
  },
  {
    "text": "factories started popping up in",
    "start": 228.56,
    "duration": 3.28
  },
  {
    "text": "countries like the uk and france during",
    "start": 229.92,
    "duration": 3.36
  },
  {
    "text": "the 1800s",
    "start": 231.84,
    "duration": 3.28
  },
  {
    "text": "right after cement was discovered as a",
    "start": 233.28,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "cheap and efficient building material",
    "start": 235.12,
    "duration": 5.199
  },
  {
    "text": "and in belgium the industry flourished",
    "start": 238.0,
    "duration": 3.92
  },
  {
    "text": "after world war one",
    "start": 240.319,
    "duration": 3.521
  },
  {
    "text": "when the country needed rebuilding and",
    "start": 241.92,
    "duration": 4.64
  },
  {
    "text": "cement tiles were an affordable option",
    "start": 243.84,
    "duration": 4.72
  },
  {
    "text": "eventually changing tastes in europe's",
    "start": 246.56,
    "duration": 3.039
  },
  {
    "text": "tile market",
    "start": 248.56,
    "duration": 4.28
  },
  {
    "text": "pushed cement aside by the mid 20th",
    "start": 249.599,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": "century",
    "start": 252.84,
    "duration": 4.04
  },
  {
    "text": "and in egypt syed says ceramic and",
    "start": 254.159,
    "duration": 3.6
  },
  {
    "text": "marble tiles",
    "start": 256.88,
    "duration": 3.359
  },
  {
    "text": "took over the market in the 1990s",
    "start": 257.759,
    "duration": 10.72
  },
  {
    "text": "shaking up his business",
    "start": 260.239,
    "duration": 10.481
  },
  {
    "text": "he says since then the high cost of",
    "start": 268.479,
    "duration": 3.361
  },
  {
    "text": "materials",
    "start": 270.72,
    "duration": 3.52
  },
  {
    "text": "and hard physical labor have steered",
    "start": 271.84,
    "duration": 4.05
  },
  {
    "text": "workers away from the craft",
    "start": 274.24,
    "duration": 4.839
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 275.89,
    "duration": 3.189
  },
  {
    "text": "uh",
    "start": 280.84,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 285.43,
    "duration": 8.17
  },
  {
    "text": "by making new cheaper designs now",
    "start": 290.16,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": "he and his two employees are among the",
    "start": 293.6,
    "duration": 5.2
  },
  {
    "text": "few tile makers left",
    "start": 295.44,
    "duration": 3.36
  },
  {
    "text": "his team can make up to 150 tiles in",
    "start": 300.08,
    "duration": 3.679
  },
  {
    "text": "just a day",
    "start": 302.56,
    "duration": 3.04
  },
  {
    "text": "they sell one square meter of them for",
    "start": 303.759,
    "duration": 3.521
  },
  {
    "text": "500 egyptian pounds",
    "start": 305.6,
    "duration": 4.27
  },
  {
    "text": "or 31 dollars to",
    "start": 307.28,
    "duration": 6.01
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 309.87,
    "duration": 3.42
  },
  {
    "text": "has been offering free apprenticeships",
    "start": 322.16,
    "duration": 4.479
  },
  {
    "text": "to young craftsmen for the past 40 years",
    "start": 323.919,
    "duration": 4.901
  },
  {
    "text": "to keep the traditional process going",
    "start": 326.639,
    "duration": 5.38
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 328.82,
    "duration": 3.199
  },
  {
    "text": "on",
    "start": 336.84,
    "duration": 9.08
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 338.98,
    "duration": 6.94
  },
  {
    "text": "but the most important thing for syed is",
    "start": 350.479,
    "duration": 3.361
  },
  {
    "text": "that this art",
    "start": 352.96,
    "duration": 3.36
  },
  {
    "text": "lives on",
    "start": 353.84,
    "duration": 2.48
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 362.46,
    "duration": 5.29
  },
  {
    "text": "inside",
    "start": 364.84,
    "duration": 14.0
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 367.75,
    "duration": 13.49
  },
  {
    "text": "foreign",
    "start": 378.84,
    "duration": 3.72
  },
  {
